plurals.name: nbViews
plurals.comment:
nbViews [one] [other]
*PLEASE READ* The number of people that viewed your blog post. It's views by IP address. So they may not be fully unique but it will usually be the number of people.
To prevent bloggers 'gaming the system', please translate it as the number of times it has been seen

resources.string: Framleis ingen innlegg i denne bloggen.
